      opts: ["Extremely well-capitalized","Highly sensitive to market interest rate changes, as purchased funds can be withdrawn if competitors offer higher yields","Highly liquid with no funding risk","Predominantly funded by stable retail deposits"],
      ans: 1, diff: "advanced",
